{"id":1649,"date":"2024-08-19T14:22:13","date_gmt":"2024-08-19T14:22:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1649"},"modified":"2024-08-19T14:22:13","modified_gmt":"2024-08-19T14:22:13","slug":"mission-007","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-007\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #007: Am I Blind?"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Mission #007: Am I Blind?<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Icicle Cave 4F, West Cavern &#8211; Ruin Maniac in front of first tablet<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Completed main story missions up until Icicle Cave<\/li>\n<li>Started <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-067\/\">Mission #067: The Food Thief<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Solve all the Ancient Tablet Puzzles in Borrius<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>5 Wishing Pieces<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<div class=\"toc-wrap\">\n<div class=\"toc-header\">\n<div class=\"toc-header__left\">\n<div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"caption\">Table of Contents<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"toc-header__right\"><button class=\"toggle-btn\">[hide]<\/button><\/div>\n<\/p><\/div>\n<div class=\"toc\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#starting_the_mission\">Starting the Mission<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#how_to_complete\">How to Complete<\/a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#tablet1\">Tablet #1 &#8211; Icicle Cave<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#tablet2\">Tablet #2 &#8211; Cinder Volcano<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#tablet3\">Tablet #3 &#8211; Valley Cave<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#tablet4\">Tablet #4 &#8211; Frost Mountain<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#tablet5\">Tablet #5 &#8211; Thundercap Mountain<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#tablet6\">Tablet #6 &#8211; Ruins of Void<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#tablet7\">Tablet #7 &#8211; Crystal Peak<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#tablet8\">Tablet #8 &#8211; Victory Road<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#tablet9\">Tablet #9 &#8211; Ruins of Void, Underwater<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#completing_the_mission\">Completing the Mission<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>After accepting a mission to find a food thief Pok\u00e9mon, and chasing it into Icicle Cave, it opens up a new passageway. Inside that passageway is a strange ancient tablet and a Ruin Maniac who wants you to solve the riddles on all 9 of them across Borrius. Do so, and he\u2019ll give you 5 Wishing Pieces.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"starting_the_mission\">Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-house-in-northeast-bellin-town.jpg\" alt=\"The house in northeast Bellin Town \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The house in northeast Bellin Town<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>In order to receive this mission, you first have to at least start <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-067\/\">Mission #067: The Food Thief<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>To do so, go to the northeast house in Bellin Town and head inside. Watch the scene play out, accept that mission, and follow the Sandslash outside.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/02-pokemon-unbound-youll-need-to-follow-the-sandslash.jpg\" alt=\"You\u2019ll need to follow the Sandslash \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>You\u2019ll need to follow the Sandslash<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You will get a message telling you that the Sandslash went off in the direction of Icicle Cave, so follow it by going north out of town and into the cave.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/03-pokemon-unbound-the-sandslash-makes-the-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"The Sandslash makes the entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Sandslash makes the entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you go inside, you\u2019ll see the Sandslash dig a hole through the cavern wall.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/04-pokemon-unbound-follow-it-through.jpg\" alt=\"Follow it through \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Follow it through<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go west from the entrance to Icicle Cave and you\u2019ll see it. It leads to another cavern entirely, and the one where you can pick up this mission.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/05-pokemon-unbound-the-mission-starts-here.jpg\" alt=\"The mission starts here \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The mission starts here<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>At the east end of the cave is an ancient tablet. <\/p>\n<p>As soon as you go to touch it, a Ruin Maniac shows up and tells you about its history.<\/p>\n<p>He gives you a <strong>Braille Converter<\/strong> so you can read what\u2019s written on it. There are nine more tablets in Borrius, and he gives you a mission to find and read them all.<\/p>\n<div class=\"callout-box\">While you can accept this mission without becoming Pok\u00e9mon Champion, you will need to do that and acquire the ADM to solve all nine tablet puzzles.<\/div>\n<h2 id=\"how_to_complete\">How to Complete<\/h2>\n<h3 id=\"tablet1\">Tablet #1 &#8211; Icicle Cave<\/h3>\n<p><strong>Requirements:<\/strong> Strength, Rock Climb<\/p>\n<p>To solve the tablet, you\u2019ll need to find a button plate somewhere in this chamber.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/06-pokemon-unbound-the-1st-tablet.jpg\" alt=\"The first tablet \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The first tablet<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go west until you\u2019re near the exit to the Alolan Sandslash area.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/07-pokemon-unbound-climb-the-wall.jpg\" alt=\"Climb the wall \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Climb the wall<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll see a rock climb wall leading up to a ledge with a Strength boulder on it. Climb up and you\u2019ll be where you need to be.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/08-pokemon-unbound-the-button-and-the-boulder.jpg\" alt=\"The button and the boulder \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The button and the boulder<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll need to use Strength to push the boulder on the button, which should be relatively straightforward but will require you to smash the upper two rocks on the ledge.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/09-pokemon-unbound-puzzle-complete.jpg\" alt=\"Puzzle complete \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Puzzle complete<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you push the boulder on the button, there\u2019ll be a huge rumbling in the cave. <\/p>\n<p>Go back down to where the tablet is.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/10-pokemon-unbound-the-1st-tablet-solved.jpg\" alt=\"The first tablet solved \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The first tablet solved<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>In the place of the tablet is now a cavern leading to a Raid Den &#8211; which means this tablet is solved.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"tablet2\">Tablet #2 &#8211; Cinder Volcano<\/h3>\n<p><strong>Requirements:<\/strong> Strength<\/p>\n<p>For the second tablet, fly to Cinder Volcano and you\u2019ll be outside the western entrance to 1F.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/11-pokemon-unbound-the-cinder-volcano-fly-point.jpg\" alt=\"The Cinder Volcano Fly point \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Cinder Volcano Fly point<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Head inside, then climb the ladder to the second floor.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/12-pokemon-unbound-head-up-to-2f.jpg\" alt=\"Head up to 2F \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Head up to 2F<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Near the hiker on the west side of the cavern is a Strength boulder.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/13-pokemon-unbound-the-boulder-is-near-the-hiker.jpg\" alt=\"The boulder is near the Hiker \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The boulder is near the Hiker<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll need to push it all the way north and east to a switch on a peninsula sticking out into the lava. <\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/14-pokemon-unbound-the-button.jpg\" alt=\"The button \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The button<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>There\u2019s no puzzle involved, it\u2019s just pushing it in a particular direction.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/15-pokemon-unbound-getting-the-boulder-to-the-button.jpg\" alt=\"Getting the boulder to the button \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Getting the boulder to the button<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you push the boulder on the button, another stepping stone will appear in the lava and you\u2019ll feel a rumbling.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/16-pokemon-unbound-cross-the-stones-and-head-north.jpg\" alt=\"Cross the stones and head north \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Cross the stones and head north<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Head across the stones in the lava until you get to the other side, then walk north.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/17-pokemon-unbound-the-2nd-tablet-is-solved.jpg\" alt=\"The second tablet is solved \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The second tablet is solved<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>There once was a tablet here &#8211; now it\u2019s gone, replaced by a Raid Den. Tablet solved.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"tablet3\">Tablet #3 &#8211; Valley Cave<\/h3>\n<p><strong>Requirements:<\/strong> Rock Climb<\/p>\n<p>Fly to Crater Town and head down into the crater to enter Valley Cave. Before you do, make sure you\u2019ve got at least one Bug-type Pok\u00e9mon in your party.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/18-pokemon-unbound-valley-cave-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"Valley Cave entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Valley Cave entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Then, once inside, go all the way south until you see a Gentleman.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/19-pokemon-unbound-the-gentleman-gives-you-a-clue.jpg\" alt=\"The Gentleman gives you a clue \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Gentleman gives you a clue<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Gentleman is above a tablet, accessible by a Rock Climb wall.<\/p>\n<p>Speak to him, and he\u2019ll tell you about the inscription. You\u2019ll need to find a switch to open the tablet, and you passed it earlier.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/20-pokemon-unbound-the-button-in-the-rock.jpg\" alt=\"The button in the rock \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The button in the rock<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>On the way to the Gentleman, right near the Pok\u00e9mon Ranger, is a rock that hides a button. <\/p>\n<p>However, you\u2019ll need to make sure that the Bug-type Pok\u00e9mon is in the first spot of your party before pressing it.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/21-pokemon-unbound-the-tablet-is-solved.jpg\" alt=\"The tablet is solved \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The tablet is solved<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>If you did things correctly, the cavern will shake. <\/p>\n<p>Head back to the Gentleman and he\u2019ll be very surprised.<\/p>\n<p>When you climb down the rock wall, you\u2019ll have access to the Raid Den now.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/22-pokemon-unbound-the-raid-den-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"The Raid Den entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Raid Den entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3 id=\"tablet4\">Tablet #4 &#8211; Frost Mountain<\/h3>\n<p><strong>Requirements:<\/strong> Rock Climb<\/p>\n<p>Fly to Frost Mountain and head on inside, walking through 1F until you reach the northwest corner.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/23-pokemon-unbound-frost-mountain-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"Frost Mountain entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Frost Mountain entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Climb the rock wall here and you\u2019ll find yourself next to the fourth tablet.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/24-pokemon-unbound-the-rock-wall.jpg\" alt=\"The rock wall \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The rock wall<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/25-pokemon-unbound-the-4th-tablet.jpg\" alt=\"The fourth tablet \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The fourth tablet<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The tablet\u2019s inscription reads \u201cENGAGING FROM BEHIND IS THE KEY\u201d, but that doesn\u2019t really make sense in this area.<\/p>\n<p>However, if you make your way to the southeast part of the cavern, it will become clear.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/26-pokemon-unbound-climb-the-rock-wall-and-youll-see-an-aggron-below.jpg\" alt=\"Climb the rock wall and you\u2019ll see an Aggron below \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Climb the rock wall and you\u2019ll see an Aggron below<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>There will be a raised platform with a big rock in the middle of it, and a rock wall on its west side. Climb it, and you\u2019ll see an Aggron below, turning and facing multiple directions rapidly.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/27-pokemon-unbound-an-unsuccessful-attempt.jpg\" alt=\"An unsuccessful attempt \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>An unsuccessful attempt<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll need to sneak up on it from behind and touch its back to solve the puzzle, but this is easier said than done. <\/p>\n<p>If the Aggron catches you, it will blow you away with a roar and you\u2019ll need to try again.<\/p>\n<p>There are two ways to do this: <\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>Become so fast, like with the Motorcycle\u2019s turbo boost, that the Aggron can\u2019t spin around in time<\/li>\n<li>Or make sure you are not dashing automatically while walking when you approach, because it will immediately spot you otherwise.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/28-pokemon-unbound-another-tablet-solved.jpg\" alt=\"Another tablet solved \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Another tablet solved<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Aggron disappears when you finally touch its back, and there will be a rumble in the cavern.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/29-pokemon-unbound-the-4th-tablet-is-open.jpg\" alt=\"The fourth tablet is open \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The fourth tablet is open<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The tablet will now be solved and the Raid Den is open.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"tablet5\">Tablet #5 &#8211; Thundercap Mountain<\/h3>\n<p><strong>Requirements:<\/strong> Rock Climb, Rock Smash, Strength, Surf<\/p>\n<p>Fly to Epidimy Town and head into Thundercap Mountain from there.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/30-pokemon-unbound-thundercap-mountain-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"Thundercap Mountain entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Thundercap Mountain entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Once you\u2019re inside, walk east until you get to the ladder to the 2F main cavern and climb it.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/31-pokemon-unbound-go-east-to-the-2f-ladder.jpg\" alt=\"Go east to the 2F ladder \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Go east to the 2F ladder<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you\u2019re on that floor, head east until you\u2019re in the middle of the cave and can see a ladder that was previously blocked by a Grunt during your first visit here.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/32-pokemon-unbound-thundercap-mt-2f.jpg\" alt=\"Thundercap Mt. 2F \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Thundercap Mt. 2F<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/33-pokemon-unbound-the-ladder-you-need-but-there-will-be-no-grunt-there-this-time.jpg\" alt=\"The ladder you need - but there will be no Grunt there this time \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The ladder you need &#8211; but there will be no Grunt there this time<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Grunt will be gone, and you are free to climb it to the Tablet Chamber on 3F.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/34-pokemon-unbound-the-ancient-tablet-gives-you-a-clue.jpg\" alt=\"The ancient tablet gives you a clue \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The ancient tablet gives you a clue<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The ancient tablet is in the center of the chamber, and it gives you the clue \u201cPRESSURE ELSEWHERE IS THE KEY\u201d.<\/p>\n<p>This puzzle needs to be solved in two parts, and the first part can be done in the Electivire Chamber on 4F.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/35-pokemon-unbound-the-ladder-to-the-electivire-chamber.jpg\" alt=\"The ladder to the Electivire Chamber \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The ladder to the Electivire Chamber<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>To get there, go south and then east across the bridge path and you\u2019ll see the ladder to 4F.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/36-pokemon-unbound-the-electivire-chamber-on-4f.jpg\" alt=\"The Electivire Chamber on 4F \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Electivire Chamber on 4F<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Once you\u2019re on the fourth floor, go south, up some stairs onto a platform and cross the bridge.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/37-pokemon-unbound-the-bridge-and-cyclist-issac.jpg\" alt=\"The bridge and Cyclist Issac \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The bridge and Cyclist Issac<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go past the cyclist until you reach another bridge leading to the northwest part of the chamber.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/38-pokemon-unbound-the-strength-puzzle-ball-in-hole.jpg\" alt=\"The strength puzzle - ball in hole \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The strength puzzle &#8211; ball in hole<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Once you cross that one you\u2019ll see a small area with a Strength boulder and a hole that it needs to be pushed into. To do that, you\u2019ll need to Rock Smash until the path is clear.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/39-pokemon-unbound-time-to-push.jpg\" alt=\"Time to push \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Time to push<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Pushing the Strength boulder in this hole solves half of the overall puzzle.<\/p>\n<p>To continue, go back all the way to the main cavern on 2F and walk to the northwest section.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/40-pokemon-unbound-the-wall-leading-to-the-northwest-chamber-section-of-2f.jpg\" alt=\"The wall leading to the Northwest Chamber section of 2F \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The wall leading to the Northwest Chamber section of 2F<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you get there, you\u2019ll see a rock wall &#8211; climb it.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/41-pokemon-unbound-the-middle-of-the-bridges.jpg\" alt=\"The middle of the bridges \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The middle of the bridges<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>This section has a lot of back-and-forth between two levels. <\/p>\n<p>Head north from where you climbed and you\u2019ll see a series of bridges.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/42-pokemon-unbound-jump-off-this-cliff-to-proceed.jpg\" alt=\"Jump off this cliff to proceed \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Jump off this cliff to proceed<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Pass the worker, then go north across the bridge, down the stairs to the west, and then down to where you have the choice of two cliffs to jump over. <\/p>\n<p>Choose the <strong>east cliff<\/strong> to proceed.<\/p>\n<p>This leads to a small stairway, another bridge, some more one-way cliff jumps to the north, and a ladder to the east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/43-pokemon-unbound-the-1st-ladder-to-3f-ignore-it.jpg\" alt=\"The first ladder to 3F - ignore it \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The first ladder to 3F &#8211; ignore it<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Ignore that ladder and go north to the two jump cliffs. Take the west one.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/44-pokemon-unbound-the-way-to-the-next-ladder.jpg\" alt=\"The way to the next ladder \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The way to the next ladder<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Follow the path northwest until you see another ladder.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/45-pokemon-unbound-pushing-boulders-to-the-next-ladder.jpg\" alt=\"Pushing boulders to the next ladder \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Pushing boulders to the next ladder<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll end up on the northern side of a chamber on 3F. You\u2019ll need to push boulders out of the way to get to the next ladder, and there are two trainers along the way as well.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/46-pokemon-unbound-continuing-on.jpg\" alt=\"Continuing on \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Continuing on<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Once you get to the next ladder, it\u2019s just a short walk across yet another bridge to find another one.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/47-pokemon-unbound-more-boulders.jpg\" alt=\"More boulders \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>More boulders<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll end up in the northeast corner on 3F, and find yourself with another boulder puzzle.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/48-pokemon-unbound-the-boulder-puzzle.jpg\" alt=\"The boulder puzzle \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The boulder puzzle<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>This one is simple enough, but requires some smashed rocks.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Step 1:<\/strong> From the starting position, <strong>push the top boulder left<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Step 2:<\/strong> Then, <strong>push the southernmost boulder you can reach south<\/strong>, revealing a smashable rock.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/49-pokemon-unbound-after-the-1st-and-2nd-moves.jpg\" alt=\"After the first and second moves \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the first and second moves<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 3:<\/strong> Turn to the east and <strong>smash the rock<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/50-pokemon-unbound-after-the-3rd-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the third move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the third move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 4:<\/strong> Go to the boulder north of where the smashed rock was and <strong>push it south<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/51-pokemon-unbound-after-the-4th-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the fourth move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the fourth move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 5:<\/strong> Push the same boulder <strong>east onto the button<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/52-pokemon-unbound-after-the-final-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the final move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the final move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>This accomplishes two things: clearing a path to the final ladder, and solving the tablet puzzle in the tablet chamber.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/53-pokemon-unbound-the-final-ladder.jpg\" alt=\"The final ladder \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The final ladder<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>With all of that done, go down the ladder.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/54-pokemon-unbound-on-the-way-out.jpg\" alt=\"On the way out \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>On the way out<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Follow the path out by jumping over the southern cliff.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/55-pokemon-unbound-the-way-out.jpg\" alt=\"The way out \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The way out<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Then, take the west cliff and you\u2019ll be able to exit the northwest section.<\/p>\n<p>Once out, go back to the tablet chamber on 3F.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/56-pokemon-unbound-the-remains-of-the-tablet.jpg\" alt=\"The remains of the Tablet \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The remains of the Tablet<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The tablet is gone, and a Raid Den entrance is in its place. The fifth tablet is solved.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"tablet6\">Tablet #6 &#8211; Ruins of Void<\/h3>\n<p><strong>Requirements:<\/strong> Pok\u00e9mon Championship, ADM<\/p>\n<p>For the sixth tablet, go to the Ruins of Void. There\u2019s a tablet in B3F, but it is actually solved from elsewhere.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/57-pokemon-unbound-arriving-at-the-ruins.jpg\" alt=\"Arriving at the Ruins \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Arriving at the Ruins<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you arrive on the landing platform, climb the rocks to the left of the cave entrance. They\u2019ll take you to the first ledge level.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/58-pokemon-unbound-the-path-to-the-dive-area.jpg\" alt=\"The path to the Dive area \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The path to the Dive area<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go west along the ledge until you see another spot for you to climb the rocks down.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/59-pokemon-unbound-a-deep-patch-of-water.jpg\" alt=\"A deep patch of water \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>A deep patch of water<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll be back down at water level, and you\u2019ll see an A-shaped deep patch of water just to the west of you.<\/p>\n<p>Surf over to the deep patch and press A &#8211; you\u2019ll be prompted to dive beneath the waves.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/60-pokemon-unbound-using-the-adm.jpg\" alt=\"Using the ADM \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using the ADM<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/61-pokemon-unbound-the-adm-submarine.jpg\" alt=\"The ADM submarine \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The ADM submarine<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Once you\u2019re underwater, go east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/62-pokemon-unbound-pass-by-a-cavern-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"Pass by a cavern entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Pass by a cavern entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You will soon pass an opening to the north. <\/p>\n<p>Keep going east, through a narrow gap.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/63-pokemon-unbound-another-ascension-point.jpg\" alt=\"Another ascension point \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Another ascension point<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>There\u2019s another spot to dive up here &#8211; ignore it and go north through another narrow passage.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/64-pokemon-unbound-the-narrow-passage.jpg\" alt=\"The narrow passage \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The narrow passage<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Keep going through the narrow passage, and it will soon widen.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/65-pokemon-unbound-the-final-ascension-point.jpg\" alt=\"The final ascension point \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The final ascension point<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When the passage gets wider, you\u2019ll see another point where you can ascend to the surface.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/66-pokemon-unbound-surface-to-the-ruins-again.jpg\" alt=\"Surface to the Ruins again \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Surface to the Ruins again<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Press B in the middle of the patch of sunlight and you\u2019ll return.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/67-pokemon-unbound-the-entrance-to-the-claydol-maze.jpg\" alt=\"The entrance to the Claydol Maze \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The entrance to the Claydol Maze<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you resurface, you\u2019ll be right next to the entrance to a new part of the ruins.<\/p>\n<p>Head on inside.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/68-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-maze.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the Maze \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the Maze<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>If you haven\u2019t been to this area before, you\u2019ll have to go through a stealth puzzle.<\/p>\n<p>The maze is filled with moving Claydol. If they spot you, they\u2019ll teleport you back to a checkpoint and you\u2019ll need to try that section again.<\/p>\n<p>Head west until you see an intersection.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/69-pokemon-unbound-take-the-south-hallway.jpg\" alt=\"Take the south hallway \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Take the south hallway<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go south, and the hallway will curve around. There will be a Claydol in this area, so be careful it does not see you.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/70-pokemon-unbound-the-switch.jpg\" alt=\"The switch \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The switch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>At the end of the passage is a switch that you\u2019ll need to push. It will then unlock a section in B3F.<\/p>\n<p>Go back there by using Dig or retracing your steps.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/71-pokemon-unbound-b3f-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"B3F entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>B3F entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>B3F is accessed through the cavern right next to the Fly point of the Ruins of Void, so it\u2019s easy enough to return to.<\/p>\n<p>At the first intersection, go north.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/72-pokemon-unbound-proceed-north-until-you-see-a-dusclops.jpg\" alt=\"Proceed north until you see a Dusclops \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Proceed north until you see a Dusclops<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Keep going north until you see a fork with Dusclops in the west passage. Without that switch, this area would have had a gate blocking it.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/73-pokemon-unbound-make-your-way-past-the-dusclops.jpg\" alt=\"Make your way past the Dusclops \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Make your way past the Dusclops<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Dusclops turn around in <strong>random directions<\/strong>, and will send you back to the beginning if they spot you. <\/p>\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Make sure you\u2019re not sprinting when you walk past them, or they will catch you immediately.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/74-pokemon-unbound-another-switch-at-the-end-of-the-passage.jpg\" alt=\"Another switch at the end of the passage \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Another switch at the end of the passage<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you make your way past all the Dusclops, you\u2019ll see another switch you need to flip.<\/p>\n<p>Do so, then make your way out of the passage and back to the intersection.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/75-pokemon-unbound-the-path-you-need-is-the-east-1.jpg\" alt=\"The path you need is the east one \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The path you need is the east one<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>From there, go north a little until you see a passage to the east. Head down it until you get to another intersection.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/76-pokemon-unbound-continue-east.jpg\" alt=\"Continue east \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Continue east<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Then, continue east to the passage that winds around. Be aware that there are Bronzong in this passage that act the same way as the Dusclops and Claydol.<\/p>\n<p>Keep going until you see another switch.<br \/>\n\u2003<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/77-pokemon-unbound-flip-the-switch.jpg\" alt=\"Flip the switch \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Flip the switch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>It is extremely difficult to flip this switch because the two Bronzong are constantly looking in different directions and one of them is usually looking where you want to go.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/78-pokemon-unbound-the-final-switch.jpg\" alt=\"The final switch \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The final switch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>However, it is the final switch, so as soon as you succeed, go back to the floor entrance.<\/p>\n<p>Then go east from the entrance intersection and you\u2019ll see a gap in the wall where a tablet once was. Tablet solved.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/79-pokemon-unbound-the-raid-den-is-open.jpg\" alt=\"The Raid Den is open \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Raid Den is open<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3 id=\"tablet7\">Tablet #7 &#8211; Crystal Peak<\/h3>\n<p><strong>Requirements:<\/strong> Pok\u00e9mon Championship<\/p>\n<p>Fly to Crystal Peak and head inside.  Then make your way to the crystal chamber.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/80-pokemon-unbound-crystal-peak-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"Crystal Peak entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Crystal Peak entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/81-pokemon-unbound-set-the-crystals.jpg\" alt=\"Set the crystals \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Set the crystals<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Activate the <strong>orange<\/strong> and <strong>yellow<\/strong> totems so only blue crystals remain.<\/p>\n<p>Then, go to the main chamber on 1F, climb down the blue crystal wall, and head to the southern blue totem.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/82-pokemon-unbound-activate-the-final-totem.jpg\" alt=\"Activate the final totem \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Activate the final totem<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Slide the blue crystal upwards and it will remove all crystal barriers from the cavern.<\/p>\n<p>Continue southeast.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/83-pokemon-unbound-the-cave-is-open.jpg\" alt=\"The cave is open \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The cave is open<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The door previously blocked by a crystal arch is now open, and you can head on inside.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/84-pokemon-unbound-stand-in-the-corner-spot.jpg\" alt=\"Stand in the corner spot \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Stand in the corner spot<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Stand in the corner of the raised platform, in the middle of the four dots, and wait there for a while. Eventually, you\u2019ll feel rumbling elsewhere in the caves.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/85-pokemon-unbound-exit-the-chamber-and-go-east.jpg\" alt=\"Exit the chamber and go east \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Exit the chamber and go east<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Leave the room and go east, surfing across a pond and then north up a waterfall.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/86-pokemon-unbound-at-the-top-of-the-waterfall.jpg\" alt=\"At the top of the waterfall \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>At the top of the waterfall<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Then once you\u2019re on the upper level, surf north to dry land and follow the path west while it loops around the rock formation in the middle.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/87-pokemon-unbound-the-raid-den-is-open.jpg\" alt=\"The Raid Den is open \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Raid Den is open<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>There used to be a tablet here, but now there\u2019s a Raid Den in its place.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"tablet8\">Tablet #8 &#8211; Victory Road<\/h3>\n<p><strong>Requirements:<\/strong> Pok\u00e9mon Championship, Surf with a Fire-type Pok\u00e9mon or ADM<\/p>\n<p>Fly to Victory Road and head inside the entrance.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/88-pokemon-unbound-victory-road-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"Victory Road entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Victory Road entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/89-pokemon-unbound-climb-the-west-rock-wall.jpg\" alt=\"Climb the west rock wall \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Climb the west rock wall<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Now that you\u2019re Pok\u00e9mon Champion, the rock wall on the west side will be accessible.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/90-pokemon-unbound-climb-down-the-ladder.jpg\" alt=\"Climb down the ladder \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Climb down the ladder<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Make your way to the ladder here and climb down to find yourself in a chamber filled with lava.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/91-pokemon-unbound-the-lava-chamber.jpg\" alt=\"The Lava Chamber \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Lava Chamber<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll need to surf into the lava to progress, so make sure you either have a Fire-type in your party or an ADM.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/92-pokemon-unbound-the-tablet.jpg\" alt=\"The tablet \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The tablet<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The tablet is on the north side of the room, and tells you to \u201cmove like a clock, and finish in the middle.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>There are five platforms with five buttons on them that you need to press in the correct order to solve this tablet.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/93-pokemon-unbound-the-1st-button.jpg\" alt=\"The first button \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The first button<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Start with the northwest button by pushing the boulder on to it. Then, continue clockwise.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/94-pokemon-unbound-the-2nd-button.jpg\" alt=\"The second button \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The second button<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Activate the northeast button, then go south to the southeast platform.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/95-pokemon-unbound-the-3rd-button.jpg\" alt=\"The third button \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The third button<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Push the boulder on the southeast button and surf across the lava west to the southwest platform.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/96-pokemon-unbound-the-4th-button.jpg\" alt=\"The fourth button \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The fourth button<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Do the same to the southwest button, and then cross the lava northeast to the center platform.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/97-pokemon-unbound-the-final-platform.jpg\" alt=\"The final platform \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The final platform<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>One final boulder to push, and you\u2019ll have solved the puzzle.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/98-pokemon-unbound-the-raid-den.jpg\" alt=\"The Raid Den \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Raid Den<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The tablet will have been destroyed and the Raid Den is open.  Only one tablet to go.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"tablet9\">Tablet #9 &#8211; Ruins of Void, Underwater<\/h3>\n<p><strong>Requirements:<\/strong> Pok\u00e9mon Championship<\/p>\n<p>Go back to the Ruins of Void underwater section you were at earlier.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/61-pokemon-unbound-the-adm-submarine.jpg\" alt=\"Return to the underwater section \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Return to the underwater section<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Then, go east until you see the cavern opening.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/99-pokemon-unbound-the-cavern-opening.jpg\" alt=\"The cavern opening \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The cavern opening<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go through it and you\u2019ll be in another section of underwater cave.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/100-pokemon-unbound-continue-northwest.jpg\" alt=\"Continue northwest \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Continue northwest<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Keep following the passage along until you find another cave entrance.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/101-pokemon-unbound-another-passage-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"Another passage entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Another passage entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go inside that one, and you\u2019ll be in another passage.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/102-pokemon-unbound-go-north-at-1st.jpg\" alt=\"Go north at first \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Go north at first<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Once you\u2019re there, head north through the seaweed and follow the passage around when it turns to the east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/103-pokemon-unbound-go-through-the-final-passage-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"Go through the final passage entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Go through the final passage entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>There\u2019s one more passage entrance you need to go through here.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/104-pokemon-unbound-the-final-stretch.jpg\" alt=\"The final stretch \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The final stretch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you\u2019re in this last chamber, go south until you see a Pok\u00e9mon.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/105-pokemon-unbound-the-toxapex.jpg\" alt=\"The Toxapex \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Toxapex<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>It\u2019s a Toxapex, and you\u2019ll need to defeat it to solve the puzzle.<\/p>\n<p>However, it won\u2019t make it easy for you, because it\u2019s at <strong>Lv.80<\/strong> and Dynamaxes itself, requiring you to fight it with two Pok\u00e9mon.<\/p>\n<p>When the Toxapex is gone, go back out of the passages until you\u2019re in the original one, then go east to follow the path you took to get to the Claydol area of the Ruins of Void.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/106-pokemon-unbound-return-to-the-east-passage.jpg\" alt=\"Return to the east passage \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Return to the east passage<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>However, instead of surfacing at that spot, go past it to the north.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/107-pokemon-unbound-the-final-tablet-is-solved.jpg\" alt=\"The final tablet is solved \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The final tablet is solved<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>This was where a tablet once was &#8211; and now it\u2019s solved, revealing a Raid Den.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"completing_the_mission\">Completing the Mission<\/h3>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/007\/108-pokemon-unbound-your-reward.jpg\" alt=\"Your reward \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Your reward<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>With all nine tablets complete, go back to the Ruin Maniac in Icicle Cave and he\u2019ll give you <strong>5 Wishing Pieces<\/strong>. This will complete the mission.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1650,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1649","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1649","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1650"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1649"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"h